This file describes the licensing terms for Pro and Enterprise features
of ArchLens. The Community Edition (CE) is licensed under MIT — see LICENSE.

Pro / Enterprise features include (but are not limited to):

- Team collaboration: shared snapshots, comments, review workflows
- CI/CD integration: build-breaking on architecture violations
- SSO / SAML authentication
- Audit logs for compliance (SOC 2, ISO 27001)
- Centralized custom rule management across repos
- Slack / Microsoft Teams notifications
- Hosted cloud option
- Priority support with SLA
- Custom integrations (ServiceNow, Jira, GitHub Enterprise)

Use of these features in production environments requires a paid license.

For licensing inquiries: archlens@example.com

